{"tid":726462,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"即食麵點煮先最好食？","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T14:48:50.000Z","uid":14055,"like":13,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"344bec6e2075dd626ac86510789f504a68cd2f2d","tid":726462,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"我一直以黎聽長輩講話即食麵餅有蠟，所以次次都過三四次水，啲麵煮到好冧冇咬口完全唔好食，係靠加晒啲調味粉先覺得比較好食&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從有日睇咗秋生教煮即食麵，個麵同凍水一齊落，一水滾就上碗，原來個時間真係啱啱好，啲麵條條彈牙，再加隻半熟蛋一齊食，又美味又便宜又快。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/195750_c341b2efcafb4945aa71839c19c927ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F195750_c341b2efcafb4945aa71839c19c927ec.png&h=ed58f6a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7f45f542af2171a2a617521ab32641208cf9f7d","tid":726462,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"巴絲一齊黎分享吓你地嘅心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5617a4f5f993aefbfa914e11692d56f87644d51a","tid":726462,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日無唔洗點飛水<br />\n<br />\n不過過冷河口感點都唔同"},{"pid":"3e1d6d2e4479945742f331f55080b98ab84ec3b4","tid":726462,"uid":13545,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"直接落味精 揸碎 乾食"},{"pid":"2f8cd2473bb11bc55fdc975be01b97b6864c733c","tid":726462,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5617a4f5f993aefbfa914e11692d56f87644d51a","tid":726462,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日無唔洗點飛水<br />\n<br />\n不過過冷河口感點都唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"煮到幾熟先過冷河？"},{"pid":"d57fd32df540b34acf46dde944c1d7a11ea261aa","tid":726462,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":11,"